## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Language | Python 3.10+ |
| Metrics collection | psutil |
| Local storage | SQLite (built-in) |
| Forecasting | statsmodels (ARIMA + Holt-Winters) |
| Data handling | pandas |
| CLI framework | Typer |
| Terminal UI | Rich |
| ASCII charts | plotext |
| Packaging | setuptools + pyproject.toml |

