## 📁 Project Structure

```
foresight/
├── foresight/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── collector.py    # psutil metrics collection
│   ├── storage.py      # SQLite database layer
│   ├── forecaster.py   # ARIMA, Holt-Winters, Ensemble, alerting
│   └── cli.py          # Typer CLI — all 8 commands
├── tests/
├── data/               # SQLite database (gitignored, created locally)
├── pyproject.toml
├── requirements.txt
├── CONTRIBUTING.md
├── LICENSE
└── README.md
```

